Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂  老妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是我  虎侍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天提早下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  收到了  裙带菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我打算最近回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什么？都好啦  什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？A种B种的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲味道的晚宴套餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑臭老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上哪有向回家的儿子索要伙食费的父母啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管你怎么做理所当然都是母亲味道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我老妈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且晚宴套餐不就是剩下的晚饭吗！你当我不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  竟然挂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那臭老太婆心情一不好就马上挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不太想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第9话\N小次郎和命运的分歧点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了没？深夜的  BAMBOO…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部团活动已经开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护面之类的  也要拿出来晒干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长套已经很破旧了吧…要换了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件制服  是同间学校的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅的话怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个  哪一个更灵验一些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想两个都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两个我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾  欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学  麻烦你把这些摆放在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看情况  来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  看你干得蛮起劲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也是很好的社会实践呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  选什么样的比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  不问我为什么在这里挑选商品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营业动力  营业动力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上啊  我打算这次放假的时候回一趟老家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老妈一大把年龄了净喜欢这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算买点什么当作礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老太婆的房间真就像这种店里的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本让人想不到是50多岁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给老妈这太贵！我去换别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾  欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  说话口气要高兴点快乐点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情也要跟着变啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  多去部团露下脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我果然还是赢不过勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  段君  给你水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃部长  让你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  荣花他的确变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有剑道的素质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在还和外行人没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却能抓住我行动的破绽  采取我难以击中的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的天质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在还毫无持久力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今后一定会突飞猛进的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在毕业前我能不被超过就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？让那种角色变强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系…那种角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你乱打一通是没法击中的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃！好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  不怕不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  校园暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对小都都做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！你用刺击还太早了！想杀人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人不准用！危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过天质不差啦  努力练习的话小都都也能变强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起干劲来了呢  真期待这次的大赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就到这里  明天再…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？打工那边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚结束  我想稍微再参加一下部团活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下  再继续练习吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看你上气不接下气的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  口渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这混杂着青春汗水中的芬芳的酱油香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  都忘了已经过三分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道场吃泡面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没吃午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙带菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你放太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  珠姬是为了我而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着去担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收礼物的时候要怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要装作若无其事地而且要表现最大限度的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太普通了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  珠姬打工真得很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那孩子太温柔  也许不想让我知道打工的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你珠姬！我打心里深爱着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行不行  不管怎么说这太肉麻了  肉麻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴啊  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变成一个好孩子爸爸太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也照这样子纯真地  脚踏实地地  美丽地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健壮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  小手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「伸手」啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（剑道的篭手（こて）与训狗用口令お手（おて）的谐音…）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来家里没酒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我正要停的车位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  但是先抢先得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  那臭老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也买些泡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡面和咖喱  还有罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是平民的好朋友啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是画里面单身汉会买的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啤酒在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一箱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！那是我正想拿走的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  但是先抢先得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么！不是摆明了硬抢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去买旁边的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的不是啤酒很贵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买一箱你也太嚣张了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个没正当职业的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买零散的足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是没正当职业的！我有正式的工作！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅  这个该死的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在收银台只开一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想绕过我抢在前面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看那个分量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他抢先的话我就要浪费很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:12:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  荞麦面你要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赔我！赔我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  我马上取新的给您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴  是这家伙不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个钱我来出…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！钱由我来出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就出给你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧…什么都别想了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种吃父母的Neet族还有脸开什么车！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是Neet！也不是没正当职业的！我是高中教师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师！少骗人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那边室江高中的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做石田虎侍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田虎侍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…这样  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？和平常一样咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学不行  怎么样都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最用功的说却不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然文系不怎么用功也能过关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉越来越讨厌  不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在玩弄我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这自觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  教我数学啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  尽管来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  说回来纪梨乃你有什么不擅长的科目吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就这样都比我高对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到齐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然老师还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始练摆振吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  段郎  给你毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真体贴呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想荣花果然是个了不起的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆振的力道越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  荣花同学会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是能毫不犹豫地进攻的人  没有多余动作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能变强的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  宫崎同学也会变强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小珠累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你打工真的很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老师来之前去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠在老师来之前休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都因为是一年级所以很轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君不管上了二年级三年级还是这么悠哉哉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊  小鞘前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不能欺负后辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你这全年级前二十的优等生给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  在说期中考试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也很惨对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  段郎是优等生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全年级390人中排名第二！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是赢不了段君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过老师还真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到的话实在太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师你什么时候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好像要消失了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的可能会消失也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能在这学校待不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长他说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教到这个学年度结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老师不就成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么校长突然这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是校长而是理事长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么理事长会亲自下命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市和一个老太婆吵了一架…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那个老太婆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长是个男人  非常温柔敦厚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理事长的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是理事长夫人说了我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么那夫人就是超市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那老太婆到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长的近邻  和理事长夫人关系超好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而理事长好像很怕老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家带好护具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从切返开始练习咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你们也稍微担心一下我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是被学校开除了  也就不能当顾问了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算我们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有用不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以去求校长不要辞退我之类…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不打算做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…像我这种没什么成就的年轻人就算说什么也没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那我们就从现在开始取得成就不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们剑道部越来越强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后进军全国大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要留下好结果  谁都无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果剑道部拿到成绩的话  也许我就能继续待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没时间了  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有川添珠姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的珠姬是无敌的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于老师则是无职的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没被开除！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！拼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中剑道部的新目标就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出赛全国大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是同等的好成绩！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  练习开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天打工就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力到最后哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始连招呼都打不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原来是拂尘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
