Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:02.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:10.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:17.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:25.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:32.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
